The Barrier Defender MKII
Replaces omen

This gun was finally remade, after two and a half months

Fires Explosives
Very high damage
High projectile count
Very high spread
Each shots fired will block off one projectile (Bullet, Rocket) and explode after
Shots will explode if it comes in contact with any surface or enemy
Slow ammo regeneration
Very deadly reload throw if thrown with a near-full mag (Can be used as a secondary attack)

Better skin than the original Barrier Defender


